324
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:28,000
Min zeman el-alem kanit tîcî tzûrû...
 
Since a long time ago people used to come visit it...

325
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,000
Min kil el-amakin?
 
From everywhere?

326
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:36,000
